{
  "stem": "12666.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Either you go on trial, even if it is not very popular, the trial, but we-- we will try you as a traitor and your family will go to prison.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or you take these pills and commit suicide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And get your papers in order.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he talked to his son, who is now the mayor of Stuttgart, and got his papers in order, took those pills, and died.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The official information was that he died of his wounds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was given a hero's burial, and you see his son is now the mayor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they had-- their-- their justice was completely different than ours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we tried to impress them that we were trying, bending, to be fair.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Naturally, many people escaped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- we didn't catch everybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even if we occupied all of Germany, they escaped because some agencies of our government were working against the Nuremberg Trial.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Like, for example, that fellow from Lyon, France, the SS man who was being used by our counter-intelligence to start getting information about the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the German courts are very lenient to these criminals.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they are not as harsh as the Nuremberg trial was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even the war crime trials in Tokyo was quite lenient.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like, for example, a Japanese general who was using PWs as guinea pigs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was given a high position and salary in the Pentagon to teach us those methods.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Nuremberg was criticized that we introduced a law that did not exist before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Michael Kremen, senior [INAUDIBLE], he says, how could you make it retroactive, crime against humanity?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the other indictments that we had, they were quite valid.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
